Description of the processor.
Useful for describing the purpose of the processor or its configuration.
</para></summary></member>
  <member key="ingest._types.CommunityIDProcessor#destination_ip"><summary><para>
Field containing the destination IP address.
</para></summary></member>
  <member key="ingest._types.CommunityIDProcessor#destination_port"><summary><para>
Field containing the destination port.
</para></summary></member>
